    "title": "Urgent Opening Real Estate Agent at Jones Lang LaSalle Digital Technologies",
    "description": "We at Jones Lang LaSalle Digital Technologies are looking for an experienced Real Estate Agent based out of Nashik. If you are a result-oriented professional with a passion for excellence, we want to hear from you.\n\nAbout Jones Lang LaSalle Digital Technologies:\nJones Lang LaSalle Digital Technologies is a leading organization in the On-site sector, committed to excellence, innovation, and employee growth. We offer a dynamic work environment where talent is recognized and rewarded.\n\nKey Responsibilities:\n• Prepare presentations and proposals for institutional clients\n• Achieve monthly and quarterly sales targets\n• Source and close property deals with prospective buyers and investors\n• Provide advisory services on property investment and market trends\n• Conduct site visits and property presentations for clients\n• Conduct market research and provide competitive analysis\n• Maintain a pipeline of qualified leads using CRM software\n\nRequired Skills & Qualifications:\n• B.Ed / M.Ed from a recognized institution\n• 12-20 years of relevant experience\n• Proficiency in Due Diligence\n• Proficiency in Market Research\n• Proficiency in Real Estate Law\n• Proficiency in CRM Software\n• Proficiency in Investment Analysis\n• Proficiency in Project Management\n• Proficiency in Negotiation Skills\n• Proficiency in MS Office\n\nWork Mode: On-site - Work from our office\n\nWhat We Offer:\n• International travel opportunities for senior roles\n• Employee stock options (ESOPs) for eligible roles\n• Learning & development budget\n• Provident Fund and Gratuity as per company policy\n• Annual performance appraisal\n• Referral bonus program\n• Salary Range: 35 LPA - 70 LPA per annum\n\nLocation: Nashik, Maharashtra, India\n\nIf you are excited about this opportunity, apply now and take the next step in your career journey with Jones Lang LaSalle Digital Technologies!",
